This world is divided.

365
00:56:40,266 --> 00:56:41,746
They are a primitive species.

366
00:56:41,920 --> 00:56:44,226
Unevolved and at war
with one another.

367
00:56:44,401 --> 00:56:47,273
Too separate to be one.

368
