1531
02:52:45,920 --> 02:52:49,271
Your father sacrificed himself
to mark that box.

1532
02:52:49,446 --> 02:52:51,446
We have to get back to my lab
and use the satellite

1533
02:52:51,491 --> 02:52:53,450
